<title>JAPAN: Japan Apr silver imports surge 62.3 pct yr/yr.</title>
<headline>Japan Apr silver imports surge 62.3 pct yr/yr.</headline>
<dateline>TOKYO 1997-05-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Japan's silver imports in April surged by 62.3 percent from a year earlier to 182.86 tonnes, Finance Ministry data released on Thursday showed.</p>
<p>The figures released by MOF were as follows (in tonnes):</p>
<p>		     Apr 97	Mar 97	Apr 96</p>
<p> Total	     182.86	91.95	 112.69</p>
<p> Major suppliers:</p>
<p> Mexico	     54.67	73.95	  36.01</p>
<p>Cumulative imports in the first four months of 1997 totalled 479.65 tonnes against 402.26 tonnes in the same period a year earlier.</p>
<p>-- Tokyo Commodity Desk +81-3-3432-7431</p>
</text>
